  <GR_OpportunitySite_AbandonedLab.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>questDescription(askerIsNull==true)-&gt;We've intercepted radio transmissions from a seemingly abandoned genetics research lab not far from [map_definite]. The site may have some interesting ancient technology scattered around, so it could be a good idea to investigate it.\n\nWe should be well prepared, as genetic monstrosities may still be roaming the derelict installation.</GR_OpportunitySite_AbandonedLab.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings.0>
